{"tid":825041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人返工返到好似跑馬仔咁","createTime":"2018-09-17T10:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T16:22:39.000Z","uid":210624,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c85aa191d0159fa090e21bd5bb5a1fd8919fe6d","tid":825041,"uid":210624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"一出閘的時候，首先帶頭的是六表嬸，她凌晨五時已到粉嶺站等頭班車。哎呀，誰知港鐵落閘，等了一整早上連站都進不了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/182842_e75375ae8eded1d8a4bb4e09d7174347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F182842_e75375ae8eded1d8a4bb4e09d7174347.jpg&h=13195d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊隨其後的是七叔，住山腰的他知道沒巴士，特意提早三小時出門口行落山，不過沿途都是塌樹，全部都是樹，七叔又忘了帶備開山刀上班，唯有在叢林中探險，希望他日落前可以出到市區吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/182901_eacb8e8c118a7f8e64f3ae20202657df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F182901_eacb8e8c118a7f8e64f3ae20202657df.jpg&h=5cb02535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉入彎位後，見到四姨婆「飆咗上嚟」，逢人過人，在上班人潮中穿來插去，來到九龍塘站，她一見到沒列車，就以9秒9的速度衝去等接駁巴士，但可惜最後都上不到車，因為根本沒有接駁巴士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/182923_1394730f31cc187f7049539ea44ca777.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F182923_1394730f31cc187f7049539ea44ca777.jpeg&h=ec16b8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來到最後大直路，一隻黑馬突然在外檔衝前，如入無人之境，直衝終點，成功返到工。<br />\n<br />\n望真啲，這隻馬的編號是「777」，由禮賓府到政府總部的距離只是1.2公里，Google Map估計需時兩至三分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/182941_1b728f541d15e8730c2606b1af26667c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F182941_1b728f541d15e8730c2606b1af26667c.png&h=55207c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事純屬創作，如有雷同，實屬不幸。<br />\n(圖片來源：蘋果日報、香港01、網上)"},{"pid":"9e75879034a3c0754a91d2ad3057e799c90bed7b","tid":825041,"uid":210624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n丹@如有雷同<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/如有雷同-522911454805837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%B7%E5%90%8C-522911454805837&d=NWcZLDcTjcZeIT4LznTpFv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ae6a2bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/如有雷同-522911454805837</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://dan.story.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdan.story.hk&d=NWcZLDcTjcZeIT4LznTpFv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fffea73c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">dan.story.hk</a><br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://danstoryhk.wixsite.com/website/blank/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdanstoryhk.wixsite.com%2Fwebsite%2Fblank%2F&d=NWcZLDcTjcZeIT4LznTpFv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f3ee6eb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://danstoryhk.wixsite.com/website/blank/</a>"},{"pid":"c22bd94c760129138229e00da519f7669097e503","tid":825041,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"馬仔今日都唔洗晨操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef469ff8790c7fea91bbeca2f5a75e208efcc7d7","tid":825041,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a743852c668932d8d93c1725acccd0070f73ae","tid":825041,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"做隻出色的馬仔"},{"pid":"bb6f8b0dd54295f52ed2e19337e77b5d6fceca47","tid":825041,"uid":210624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬仔今日都唔洗晨操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地連馬都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後明天賽事又繼續"},{"pid":"f2f192f7f6a3bb4457feae2a0ecab6203f25453e","tid":825041,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"想學跑馬但又的的了了做乜鳩<br />\n不倫不類"},{"pid":"e46eb43176e4f319647533b0c604d955ab567ac4","tid":825041,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d83b9feb4e06474468a3334c46915e093c056393","tid":825041,"uid":185449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"唉 好撚尷尬 見你比心機打咁多廢話 唔忍心負皮..."}]}